responseText: NSLOCTEXT("[70199B914E7E03A9706A1499CF20B1FD]", "F4A92D414FE37A2219FF16B7675BE0E7", "This limp scrap of weird paper is a note. It claims that the Hoarders in Carphin are hapless thieves, transmuted by the Guardsmen of old then forgotten long ago. The note contains a request that this last bit be burned in the Watchman\'s Light at the peak of Carphin Isle after the Hoarders have been avenged.")
